---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Work with me – Nazar Gladish"
  description="I book qualified sales meetings for founders and agencies that sell high-value services. You only pay if I deliver. No strings."
>
  <main id="main-content" data-layout="work">
    <header>
      <h1>
        I book you sales meetings.<br />You only pay if I deliver. No strings.
      </h1>
    </header>

    <section class="section">
      <p>
        For founders and agencies that sell high&#8209;value work and are done
        chasing pipeline. I build the outreach, I run it, and you only hear from
        me when there's a meeting on your calendar.
      </p>

      <p>
        It all runs on Kestrel, a system I built and don't sell. It watches the
        whole market for the moment a company becomes a buyer: a fresh raise, a
        new exec, a hiring surge. Then it reaches out, in your name, before
        anyone else does. You never see the machine. You just take the calls it
        books.
      </p>

      <p>
        I taught myself to code, passed the senior&#8209;engineer trial at <a
          href="https://github.com/antiwork"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">Gumroad</a
        >, shipped to a platform with 7M monthly users, and worked inside one of
        the biggest names in outbound. I built the system, and I run every
        campaign myself. I only win when you do.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="cta">
      <p>
        I take on a few clients at a time. Tell me what you sell, and I'll show
        you the meetings you're missing.
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href="mailto:hi@nazargladish.com?subject=Book%20me%20meetings"
          >hi@nazargladish.com</a
        >
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<script>
  document.addEventListener("astro:page-load", () => {
    const layout = (document.querySelector("#main-content") as HTMLElement)
      ?.dataset?.layout;
    if (layout) {
      sessionStorage.setItem("backUrl", "/work");
    }
  });
</script>

<style>
  main {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 24px 4rem;
  }
  header h1 {
    line-height: 1.25;
  }
  .section {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  .cta {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }
</style>
